                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210411-115-off711 t18210411-115-cd712"></join>, 66 lbs. of lead, value 7 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210411-115-victim1267" type="victimName">
